<div class="title">Sweating, Sweating, Sweating</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=freezing+too&Exact=1">freezing too</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; freezing too. "Sweating, Sweating, Sweating: An Experience with Amanita muscaria (exp4338)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 24, 2000. erowid.org/exp/4338</div>

<br/>



